{"tid":1931553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐港領事館暫停所有移民簽證！","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T07:46:40.000Z","uid":228995,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcc27935191f9f0935c7d3d6c0fc596f5219cf8","tid":1931553,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n由3月19日起 ，美國駐香港及澳門總領事館，會暫停所有常規嘅移民及非移民簽證服務。更改預約無須缴費，簽證費用會有效一年。我地嘅美國公民服務部會繼續提供所有服務，詳情: <a href=\"https://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk/index.html?firstTime=No\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ustraveldocs.com%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3FfirstTime%3DNo&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=b47ff5a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk/index.html?firstTime=No</a> <br />\nStarting March 19, the U.S. Consulate General in Hong Kong and Macau is suspending all routine immigrant and nonimmigrant visa services. There is no fee to change an appointment and visa application fees are valid for one year. Please monitor our website for updates. Our American Citizen Services unit will continue to provide the full range of services. Details: <a href=\"https://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk/index.html?firstTime=No\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ustraveldocs.com%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3FfirstTime%3DNo&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=b47ff5a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk/index.html?firstTime=No</a><br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n雖然只係因為關武漢肺炎事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d86e4fc1406ab20fbf2c3fbf914509d92a4561","tid":1931553,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n